profile:
PARKIS - Easy and Smart Bicycle Parking!
The idea of PARKIS was born out of the desire to find a bike storage solution, which would save space and be easy to use. All available bike storage ideas like bike racks, bike hooks, bike stands, bike trees or wall mounts, all had one thing in common – THEY ALL REQUIRED PHYSICAL EFFORT TO STORE THE BIKE. 

PARKIS is THE FIRST AND ONLY non-electric, fully mechanized bicycle storage system on the market that vertically stores bikes without any physical effort. The user has to simply guide the front wheel into the parking cradle and PARKIS does the rest. It is the easiest and most convenient way to save on storage space for one, or several bicycles.

This vertical bicycle lift is designed so that it can be used with the most popular bikes. Only these criteria apply:
Tire width from 38 mm (1.5″) to 51 mm (2.4″)
Wheel diameter 61 cm (24″) or more
Weight on front axis up to 15 kg (33 lb)
specialities:
PARKIS-an easy and smart bicycle parking! It is an automatized bicycle parking lift, which allows you to vertically park your bicycle without any physical efforts. PARKIS lets you free up precious storage floor space at home, in your office, garage or balcony. It is eco-friendly, entirely mechanical equipment, which does not require electricity. Patent pending.

Easy to use,
Space saving,
Unique design,
Needs no electricity,
Quick installation,
Maintenance free.
name: Bike Storage Solutions
